spacesuit-paramedic-hardsuit-name = Sanitater hardsuit
spacesuit-paramedic-hardsuit-desc = A modular hardsuit with heavier plates to shrug off a bullet or two, hopefully.

spacesuit-security-voidsuit-name = Security voidsuit
spacesuit-security-voidsuit-desc = A light voidsuit with an in-built plate carrier to provide moderate protection while remaining mobile.

spacesuit-security-hardsuit-name = Security 'dragoon' hardsuit
spacesuit-security-hardsuit-desc = A modular hardsuit with ceramic inserts to provide more protection than the voidsuit counterpart, but with less mobility.

spacesuit-headofsecurity-voidsuit-name = Head of security's voidsuit
spacesuit-headofsecurity-voidsuit-desc = A light voidsuit with material cut from non-vital areas to slightly increase the armour value of the vital organs.

spacesuit-headofsecurity-hardsuit-name = Head of security's 'bulwark' hardsuit
spacesuit-headofsecurity-hardsuit-desc = A modular hardsuit with expensive plastitanium armour for the head of security's use.

spacesuit-engineer-voidsuit-name = Engineering voidsuit
spacesuit-engineer-voidsuit-desc = A light voidsuit for low-intensity repairs around the station

spacesuit-engineer-hardsuit-name = Engineering 'sapper' hardsuit
spacesuit-engineer-hardsuit-desc = A modular hardsuit with increased blast plating and the large visor replaced with external cameras to better protect against explosions.